sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant R as LlmResponseProcessor
    participant T as TerminalManager
    participant D as TerminalDaemonClient
    participant X as Terminal Daemon
    participant O as Output Channel

    R->>T: enqueue(명령)
    T->>T: isLongRunningDevCommand(cmd) = true
    T->>T: _queuePausedForLongRunning = true
    T->>D: run(cmd)
    D->>X: JSONL 요청
    X-->>D: 장시간 스트림
    D->>O: 실시간 로그 기록
    note over T: 종료/중단 시 큐 재개
